{"word":"H6754 - צֶלֶם - tselem - tseh'-lem - Image","slug":"H6754","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">צֶלֶם</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>tselem"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>tseh'-lem"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Image"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E6;&#x05DC;&#x05DD; - tselem</b> - <i>tseh'-lem</i><p/>From an unused root meaning to <i>shade</i>; a <i>phantom</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>illusion</i>, <i>resemblance</i>; hence a representative <i>figure</i>, especially an <i>idol: - </i>image, vain shew."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H6756\">H6756</a>, <a href=\"#/H6758\">H6758</a>, <a href=\"#/H6759\">H6759</a>"}]}